title: Carberp online banking trojan source code leak
description:
This torrent contains the source code of the Carberp online banking trojan which was leaked in June 2013. See the thread on TrojanForge.com [1] for more details. I've downloaded the stuff from there and created a torrent because download links on one-click-hosters typically don't stay online very long.

Please note that I don't have a very fast Internet connection and so the initial seeding will probably take one day or so.

[1]: http://trojanforge.com/showthread.php?t=5229
